<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Mind Over Medal</title>
  <style>
    body {
      margin: 0;
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      background-color: #f7faff;
      color: #0a3d62;
      scroll-behavior: smooth;
    }

    header {
      background-color: #0a3d62;
      color: white;
      padding: 20px;
      text-align: center;
    }

    nav {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      gap: 20px;
      margin-top: 10px;
    }

    nav a {
      color: white;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: bold;
      transition: color 0.3s;
    }

    nav a:hover {
      color: #74b9ff;
    }

    section {
      min-height: 100vh;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      justify-content: center;
      align-items: center;
      padding: 50px;
      opacity: 0;
      transform: translateY(50px);
      transition: all 1s ease;
    }

    section.show {
      opacity: 1;
      transform: translateY(0);
    }

    .contact {
      background-color: #dfefff;
      border-radius: 10px;
      padding: 20px;
    }

    img {
      max-width: 500px;
      border-radius: 10px;
      margin: 20px 0;
    }

    footer {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 20px;
      background-color: #0a3d62;
      color: white;
    }

    a.link {
      color: #0a3d62;
      text-decoration: underline;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <header>
    <h1>Mind Over Medal</h1>
    <nav>
      <a href="#about">About</a>
      <a href="#impact">Impact</a>
      <a href="#resources">Resources</a>
      <a href="#contact">Contact</a>
    </nav>
  </header>

  <section id="about">
    <h2>About Mind Over Medal</h2>
    <p>
      Athletes often face immense pressure, both physically and mentally. 
      Mental health plays a critical role in sports performance, recovery, and overall well-being. 
      “Mind Over Medal” explores the importance of psychological strength alongside physical skill.
    </p>
    <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1517649763962-0c623066013b" alt="Athlete meditating before competition">
  </section>

  <section id="impact">
    <h2>The Impact of Mental Health on Athletes</h2>
    <p>
      Poor mental health can lead to burnout, anxiety, depression, and reduced performance. 
      Many elite athletes, including Olympians, have spoken out about their struggles, 
      highlighting the importance of support and awareness.
    </p>
    <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1508780709619-79562169bc64" alt="Sports stress and focus">
  </section>

  <section id="resources">
    <h2>Learn More</h2>
    <p>Here are some resources that discuss mental health in sports:</p>
    <ul>
      <li><a class="link" href="https://www.ncaa.org/sports/2016/7/20/mental-health.aspx" target="_blank">NCAA: Mental Health in Student-Athletes</a></li>
      <li><a class="link" href="https://www.who.int/news-room/fact-sheets/detail/mental-health-strengthening-our-response" target="_blank">WHO on Mental Health</a></li>
      <li><a class="link" href="https://www.apa.org/monitor/2021/07/athletes-mental-health" target="_blank">APA: Supporting Athletes’ Mental Health</a></li>
    </ul>
    <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1584466977773-e625c2c0f2d5" alt="Team support in sports">
  </section>

  <section id="contact">
    <h2>Contact Us</h2>
    <div class="contact">
      <p>Email: <a class="link" href="mailto:dia16160@diaestudents.com">dia16160@diaestudents.com</a></p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <footer>
    <p>&copy; 2025 Mind Over Medal | Raising Awareness for Athlete Mental Health</p>
  </footer>

  <script>
    // Slide-in animation on scroll
    const sections = document.querySelectorAll("section");
    const observer = new IntersectionObserver(entries => {
      entries.forEach(entry => {
        if (entry.isIntersecting) {
          entry.target.classList.add("show");
        }
      });
    }, { threshold: 0.2 });

    sections.forEach(section => {
      observer.observe(section);
    });
  </script>
</body>
</html>
